首先，需要确定光源布置的方案，可以采用一排等间隔的LED光源。假设每个LED光源的功率为1mW，空间中共布置了100个光源。

接下来，需要进行光场传输计算，以确定接收功率和波动情况。可以采用MATLAB中的光学传输矩阵法（Optical Transfer Matrix, OTM）进行计算。

以下是MATLAB代码：

```
%% parameters
wavelength = 1550e-9; % 波长
k = 2*pi/wavelength; % 波数
NA = 0.2; % 数值孔径
pitch = 2e-3; % LED间距
N = 100; % LED数
power = 1e-3; % 光源功率
distance = 1; % 光传输距离
R = 0.2; % 接收器半径
Np = 10000; % 采样点数目

%% build OTM
f_L = @(theta) NA*sin(theta); % 焦距函数
theta_max = asin(NA);
theta = linspace(0, theta_max, N);
y = (0:N-1)*pitch - (N-1)*pitch/2;
[X,Y] = meshgrid(y,y);
x = reshape(X, 1, []);
y = reshape(Y, 1, []);
z = zeros(1, N^2);
o = ones(1, N^2);
A = [x', y', z', o', o', o'];
B = [o', o', o', -f_L(theta)', tan(theta)', o'];
C = [o', o', z'+distance, o', o', o'];
D = [o', o', -k*cos(theta)', o', o', k*sin(theta)'];
OTM = [A; B; C; D];

%% calculate power distribution at receiver
dx = 2*R/(sqrt(Np)-1);
[Xp,Yp] = meshgrid(-R:dx:R, -R:dx:R);
rp = sqrt(Xp.^2 + Yp.^2);
thetap = atan2(Yp, Xp);
thetam = theta';
phi = ones(size(rp)).*exp(-1j*k*distance)./rp;
OTMp = [Xp(:), Yp(:), zeros(Np, 1), ones(Np, 1), zeros(Np, 1), zeros(Np, 1)];
OTMf = OTM*OTMp.';
Am = exp(1j*k*(rp(:)*thetam(:)'));
Ap = Am*OTMf;
Pp = abs(Ap.'*phi(:)).^2;
Pr = sum(Pp)*dx^2;
Pmax = max(Pp);
Pmin = min(Pp);
Pmean = mean(Pp);
PD = 10*log10(Pmax/Pmin);
```

代码中，首先定义了光源的参数，包括波长、数值孔径、LED间距、光源功率等；接着，通过构建光学传输矩阵，计算了光场在接收器平面上的功率分布。最后，计算了接收功率、最大功率、最小功率、平均功率以及功率波动。

